               <p>MESSRS. BRODERICK and PRENDERGAST conducted the prosecution.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18210214-126-person1282">
                  JOHN 
                  TAYLOR
               <interp inst="t18210214-126-person1282" type="surname" value="TAYLOR"></interp>
